{"pageProps":{"post":{"attributes":{"description":"Build a simple visual interface for viewing and editing permission rules."},"html":"<h1>Visual Editor UI</h1>\n<p>Let&#39;s build a simple admin UI for managing permissions.</p>\n<h2>Live Code: Permission List Component</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-tsx\"><button class=\"copy-btn\">Copy</button><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// client/src/admin/PermissionList.tsx</span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> { useState, useEffect } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;react&quot;</span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">interface</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">PermissionRule</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">id</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">number</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">type</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;allow&quot;</span> | <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;deny&quot;</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">role</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">string</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">action</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">string</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">subject</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">string</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">conditions</span>?: <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Record</span>&lt;<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">string</span>, <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">string</span>&gt;\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">fields</span>?: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">string</span>[]\n}\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">PermissionList</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> [rules, setRules] = useState&lt;<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">PermissionRule</span>[]&gt;([])\n\n  <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">useEffect</span>(<span class=\"hljs-function\">() =&gt;</span> {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">fetch</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;/api/admin/permissions&quot;</span>)\n      .<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">then</span>(<span class=\"hljs-function\">(<span class=\"hljs-params\">r</span>) =&gt;</span> r.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">json</span>())\n      .<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">then</span>(setRules)\n  }, [])\n\n  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> (\n    <span class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">className</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;permission-list&quot;</span>&gt;</span>\n      <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">h2</span>&gt;</span>Permission Rules<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">h2</span>&gt;</span>\n\n      <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">table</span>&gt;</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">thead</span>&gt;</span>\n          <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">tr</span>&gt;</span>\n            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">th</span>&gt;</span>Type<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">th</span>&gt;</span>\n            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">th</span>&gt;</span>Role<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">th</span>&gt;</span>\n            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">th</span>&gt;</span>Action<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">th</span>&gt;</span>\n            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">th</span>&gt;</span>Subject<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">th</span>&gt;</span>\n            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">th</span>&gt;</span>Conditions<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">th</span>&gt;</span>\n            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">th</span>&gt;</span>Fields<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">th</span>&gt;</span>\n            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">th</span>&gt;</span>Actions<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">th</span>&gt;</span>\n          <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">tr</span>&gt;</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">thead</span>&gt;</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">tbody</span>&gt;</span>\n          {rules.map((rule) =&gt; (\n            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">tr</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">key</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">{rule.id}</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">className</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">{rule.type}</span>&gt;</span>\n              <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">td</span>&gt;</span>{rule.type}<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">td</span>&gt;</span>\n              <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">td</span>&gt;</span>{rule.role}<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">td</span>&gt;</span>\n              <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">td</span>&gt;</span>{rule.action}<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">td</span>&gt;</span>\n              <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">td</span>&gt;</span>{rule.subject}<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">td</span>&gt;</span>\n              <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">td</span>&gt;</span>{JSON.stringify(rule.conditions) || &quot;-&quot;}<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">td</span>&gt;</span>\n              <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">td</span>&gt;</span>{rule.fields?.join(&quot;, &quot;) || &quot;all&quot;}<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">td</span>&gt;</span>\n              <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">td</span>&gt;</span>\n                <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">button</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">onClick</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">{()</span> =&gt;</span> handleEdit(rule)}&gt;Edit<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">button</span>&gt;</span>\n                <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">button</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">onClick</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">{()</span> =&gt;</span> handleDelete(rule.id)}&gt;Delete<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">button</span>&gt;</span>\n              <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">td</span>&gt;</span>\n            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">tr</span>&gt;</span>\n          ))}\n        <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">tbody</span>&gt;</span>\n      <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">table</span>&gt;</span>\n\n      <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">button</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">onClick</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">{()</span> =&gt;</span> setShowModal(true)}&gt;Add Rule<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">button</span>&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n  )\n}\n</code></pre><h2>Styling</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-css\"><button class=\"copy-btn\">Copy</button><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.permission-list</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">tr</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.allow</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#e6ffe6</span>;\n}\n<span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.permission-list</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">tr</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.deny</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#ffe6e6</span>;\n}\n</code></pre><p>The list shows all rules with visual distinction between allow (green) and deny (red).</p>\n","markdown":"\n# Visual Editor UI\n\nLet's build a simple admin UI for managing permissions.\n\n## Live Code: Permission List Component\n\n```tsx\n// client/src/admin/PermissionList.tsx\n\nimport { useState, useEffect } from \"react\"\n\ninterface PermissionRule {\n  id: number\n  type: \"allow\" | \"deny\"\n  role: string\n  action: string\n  subject: string\n  conditions?: Record<string, string>\n  fields?: string[]\n}\n\nexport function PermissionList() {\n  const [rules, setRules] = useState<PermissionRule[]>([])\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    fetch(\"/api/admin/permissions\")\n      .then((r) => r.json())\n      .then(setRules)\n  }, [])\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"permission-list\">\n      <h2>Permission Rules</h2>\n\n      <table>\n        <thead>\n          <tr>\n            <th>Type</th>\n            <th>Role</th>\n            <th>Action</th>\n            <th>Subject</th>\n            <th>Conditions</th>\n            <th>Fields</th>\n            <th>Actions</th>\n          </tr>\n        </thead>\n        <tbody>\n          {rules.map((rule) => (\n            <tr key={rule.id} className={rule.type}>\n              <td>{rule.type}</td>\n              <td>{rule.role}</td>\n              <td>{rule.action}</td>\n              <td>{rule.subject}</td>\n              <td>{JSON.stringify(rule.conditions) || \"-\"}</td>\n              <td>{rule.fields?.join(\", \") || \"all\"}</td>\n              <td>\n                <button onClick={() => handleEdit(rule)}>Edit</button>\n                <button onClick={() => handleDelete(rule.id)}>Delete</button>\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n          ))}\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n\n      <button onClick={() => setShowModal(true)}>Add Rule</button>\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n```\n\n## Styling\n\n```css\n.permission-list tr.allow {\n  background: #e6ffe6;\n}\n.permission-list tr.deny {\n  background: #ffe6e6;\n}\n```\n\nThe list shows all rules with visual distinction between allow (green) and deny (red).\n","slug":"visual-editor-ui","title":"Visual Editor Ui","section":"Permission Editor UI","icon":"edit","filePath":"/home/runner/work/fem-permission-systems-that-scale/fem-permission-systems-that-scale/lessons/08-permission-editor/C-visual-editor-ui.md","nextSlug":"/fem-permission-systems-that-scale/lessons/permission-editor/rule-editor-modal","prevSlug":"/fem-permission-systems-that-scale/lessons/permission-editor/permission-storage"}},"__N_SSG":true}